    <text id="A8058T">
        <front id="d2">
            <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
                <p>Trotter asks McCue for help in raising money to alleviate Trotter's debt.</p>
            </div1>
        </front>

        <body id="d4">
            <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
                <head>
                    <abbr expan="James">J.</abbr> J. A. Trotter
                </head>

                <opener>
                    <dateline>
                        <date value="1860-10-30"><abbr expan="October">Oct</abbr> 30<hi
                                rend="underline">th</hi> 1860</date>
                        <name type="place">Staunton</name>
                    </dateline>
                    <salute>John H. McCue Esq<hi rend="underline">r</hi><lb/><abbr expan="Dear"
                        >D.</abbr> Sir</salute>
                </opener>

                <p>I Suppose you will think I. am <orig reg="troublesome">tobblesome</orig> but it
                    is <orig reg="necessity">neddsesaty</orig> that makes me write to you <orig
                        reg="again">a gain</orig> I. am hard up and <orig reg="compelled"
                    >compeld</orig> to raise Some money or have my property Sold by the Sheriff is
                        <orig reg="there">thare</orig>
                    <orig reg="any">annay</orig> way by which you can <orig reg="help">healp</orig>
                    me Some you wrote to me that you expected to make Some arrangement to get Some
                    money it <orig reg="would">wood</orig> be a very <orig reg="great">grate</orig>
                    accomodation to me at this time if you could do Something for me</p>

                <closer>
                    <salute>Very <orig reg="Respectfully">Respetfully</orig></salute>
                    <signed><abbr expan="James">Jas</abbr> J. A. Trotter</signed>
                </closer>
            </div1>
        </body>
    </text>
